      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    COVID-19: guidance for the safe use of places of worship and special religious services and gatherings during the pandemic
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Guidance to enable the safe reopening of places of worship for a broader range of activities and includes a checklist for special religious services and gatherings.</p>

  </div>
</div>

